  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/4c3768a846e0a96ce8adf1099add0c5c.avif?t=1726520686\" width=640 height=82 /></span><br>In the game \"<i>Mannequin machine</i>\" you have to try yourself as a beginner in a mannequin factory. Your task is to last 6 shifts. Be careful, because this place is not what it seems, and is fraught with its own terrible secrets that you have to find out.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/ff836dd7510cda4286fd406fba8721e4.poster.avif?t=1726520686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/ff836dd7510cda4286fd406fba8721e4.webm?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/ff836dd7510cda4286fd406fba8721e4.mp4?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The main task during the shift is to fulfill the plan and produce the required number of mannequins. But it is necessary to carefully monitor each batch, because it may contain defective mannequins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/c5e09ec9897a7f7554b279f472570133.poster.avif?t=1726520686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/c5e09ec9897a7f7554b279f472570133.webm?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/c5e09ec9897a7f7554b279f472570133.mp4?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use a mask and do not move when danger is nearby, because <strong>IT</strong> is looking for people among the mannequins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/737779de6199e246a347554791aecb85.poster.avif?t=1726520686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/737779de6199e246a347554791aecb85.webm?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/737779de6199e246a347554791aecb85.mp4?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Look for notes revealing the secrets of this place. Some mannequins want to help and warn you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/2516b09369d52a31305bd3fd4ebc3b97.poster.avif?t=1726520686\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/2516b09369d52a31305bd3fd4ebc3b97.webm?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101180/extras/2516b09369d52a31305bd3fd4ebc3b97.mp4?t=1726520686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>-Unusual gameplay<br>-Realistic and atmospheric graphics<br>-High quality sounds<br>-Multiple endings",
